Presidential Adviser:
He will speak out when he
believes his voice

00:27.995 --> 00:33.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
can move the needle, make a
difference and
be an inspiration to those who
are looking

00:33.100 --> 00:35.002 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
for positive change in our
country.

00:35.035 --> 00:40.807 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And how one
sculptor is breaking
down barriers with art that
questions identity

00:40.841 --> 00:42.876 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in a globalized, modern world.

00:42.910 --> 00:48.615 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
YINKA SHONIBARE, Sculptor: A lot
of the figures
are of a mixed race.

00:48.649 --> 00:51.919 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
