Clinton says
it hurt her chances.

02:54.041 --> 02:58.445 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The nominee for
U.S. housing
secretary defended his
qualifications for

02:58.478 --> 03:01.214 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the job today at his
confirmation hearing.

03:01.248 --> 03:08.121 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Dr. Ben Carson, a former
pediatric neurosurgeon,
said after growing up poor in
inner-city Detroit,

03:08.155 --> 03:11.091 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
