pressed Carson
to guarantee that federal
housing funds won't

03:17.097 --> 03:19.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
go to help the Trump family's
real estate
business.

03:19.766 --> 03:21.568 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

03:21.601 --> 03:22.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BEN CARSON, Housing and Urban
Development
Secretary Nominee: It will not
be my intention

03:22.602 --> 03:25.305 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to do anything to benefit any --
any American.

03:25.338 --> 03:26.540 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

03:26.573 --> 03:28.275 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
ELIZABETH WARREN (D),
Massachusetts: I understand
that

03:28.308 --> 03:29.543 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

03:29.576 --> 03:30.277 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
BEN CARSON: It's for all
Americans, everything
that we do.

03:30.310 --> 03:32.212 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

03:32.245 --> 03:36.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH WARREN: But do I take
that to mean
that you may manage programs
that will significantly

03:36.049 --> 03:37.918 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
benefit the president-elect?

03:37.951 --> 03:39.619 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

03:39.653 --> 03:42.722 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BEN CARSON: You can take it to
mean that I
will manage things in a way that
benefits

03:42.756 --> 03:44.224 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the American people.

03:44.257 --> 03:46.159 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
That is going to be the goal.

03:46.193 --> 03:50.363 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Also today, the
president-elect
tapped Rudy Giuliani to advise
his administration

03:50.397 --> 03:52.165 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on cyber-security.

03:52.199 --> 03:56.570 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
