some Ram pickups
and Jeep Grand Cherokees emit
more pollution

05:32.933 --> 05:34.267 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
than federal law allows.

05:34.301 --> 05:38.238 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Just yesterday, Volkswagen
pleaded guilty
to emissions cheating.

05:38.271 --> 05:43.176 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: Americans who
really want Obamacare
repealed started to get what
they want this

05:43.210 --> 05:44.744 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
morning.

05:44.778 --> 05:48.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
