don't really
do agriculture or nothing.

06:38.265 --> 06:42.369 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, it's just kind of a -- until
it flows
out, man, I just got a big lake
in my backyard

06:42.402 --> 06:44.204 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
for now.

06:44.237 --> 06:47.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Forecasters
expect the rainfall
in Northern California to taper
off after

06:47.173 --> 06:49.209 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
today.

