07:43.930 --> 07:52.272 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
STEVE INSKEEP: Now,
President-elect Trump
has said he would like to
improve relations

07:52.305 --> 07:53.807 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with Russia.

07:53.840 --> 07:58.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
