views Russia
as America's number one threat.

07:58.712 --> 07:59.746 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Let's listen to General James
Mattis at his
hearing today.

07:59.779 --> 08:01.614 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GEN.

08:01.648 --> 08:04.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES MATTIS (RET.), Secretary
of Defense
Nominee: I would consider the
principal threats

08:04.050 --> 08:07.687 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to start with Russia.

08:07.721 --> 08:14.561 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
