nations nearby them,
whether it be with weapons of
mass destruction

08:20.467 --> 08:27.474 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or I would call it unusual,
unorthodox means
of intimidating them.

08:27.507 --> 08:30.744 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: Well, let's talk
about this
with Michael McFaul, who served
as ambassador

08:30.777 --> 08:33.913 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
