Farkas, who served
as deputy assistant secretary of
defense for

08:45.225 --> 08:48.528 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Russia, Ukraine and Eurasia from
2012 to 2015.

08:48.561 --> 08:52.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She's now a senior fellow at the
Atlantic
Council, which is a Washington
security think

08:52.699 --> 08:53.666 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
tank.

08:53.700 --> 08:54.801 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And welcome to you both.

08:54.834 --> 08:56.202 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And, Evelyn, let's start with
you.

08:56.236 --> 08:58.938 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
