Carolina, it's
not ISIS?

09:01.307 --> 09:03.476 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
EVELYN FARKAS, Former Defense
Department Official:
Nope, it's not the others.

09:03.510 --> 09:06.579 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Actually, what is interesting
is, he mentioned
Russia by name.

09:06.613 --> 09:08.615 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
